item.title: Starting with React- Factorial react Component
item.description: React is an Open Source, client-side web library for building composable user interfaces developed by Facebook and Instagram. The Instagram website, Facebook’s comment and like components are developed with React. React home pageÂ provides code samples that run live and give results just next to it. The getting started page provides necessary documentation and has a download link for the Starter Kit that’s a convenient package that includes HTML templates, the React libraries and this set of examples.
